        - Johnson, Steven L., Eddy, Sean R. & Portugaly, Elon.
          *Hidden Markov model speed heuristic and iterative HMM search
          procedure*. BMC Bioinformatics 11, 431 (18 August 2010).
          :doi:`10.1186/1471-2105-11-431`.

